{"tid":2477051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又面癱 67歲市民狠批政府","createTime":"2021-04-06T03:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:48:42.000Z","uid":98431,"like":316,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"a3bb50947ec632cbda6f64aa2d40d4b1c6c281cd","tid":2477051,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"再有市民接種科興疫苗後出現面癱！一名67歲男子在上月26日接種第2劑科興疫苗後，出現面癱及歪臉，肌肉不能自我控制，他狠批港府不理市民死活，認為年紀大不宜接種疫苗。衞生署回覆<span class=\"red\">東網</span>查詢證實此事，指上月30日接獲醫管局呈報1宗懷疑貝爾面癱的報告，根據資料，涉事男子曾於上月26日接種第二劑新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">讀者馮先生</span>表示，自己過往身體健康良好，日常會行山及游水，他於2月26日及上月26日接種科興疫苗，惟上月29日起開始流眼水，翌日出現面癱、眼皮下垂、流鼻水及臉歪等，肌肉不能自我控制，嚴重影響日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.yahoo.com/home/67-歲翁打第二劑科興四日後面癱-狠批政府懶理港人死活-014105567.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F67-%E6%AD%B2%E7%BF%81%E6%89%93%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%8A%91%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E5%9B%9B%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%99%B1-%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%B6%E7%90%86%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E6%B4%BB-014105567.html&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=257a0101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.yahoo.com/home/67-歲翁打第二劑科興四日後面癱-狠批政府懶理港人死活-014105567.html</a>"},{"pid":"f9fc01b005278de69778c8ae9c42d4079f777a6b","tid":2477051,"uid":331739,"like":233,"dislike":1,"score":232,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"咁你不滿又可以點啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb122d927c70620fe28bf451649573152a7700e","tid":2477051,"uid":17641,"like":339,"dislike":1,"score":338,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"收左美國佬錢搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bf86cb5eac25e0f56d70a11a9836f24ffc3eb0","tid":2477051,"uid":98431,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"f9fc01b005278de69778c8ae9c42d4079f777a6b","tid":2477051,"uid":331739,"like":233,"dislike":1,"score":232,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"20